# Puchi Backend

Monorepo Go microservices với **Kratos v3**. 7 service modules trong `app/`, workspace qua `go.work`.

## Tech Stack

| Thành phần | Công nghệ |
|------------|-----------|
| Ngôn ngữ | Go 1.26 |
| Framework | Kratos v3 (HTTP/gRPC hybrid, Protobuf-first) |
| DI | Wire (compile-time) |
| Auth | Supertoken (self-host) |
| Database | PostgreSQL 18 (CloudNativePG) |
| Cache | Valkey/Redis |
| Message Queue | NATS (event-driven) |
| Object Storage | Garage (S3 API) |
| Migration | goose |

## Cấu trúc monorepo

```
puchi-backend/
├── api/                           # Protobuf definitions CHUNG
│   ├── auth/v1/
│   ├── content/v1/
│   └── ...
├── app/                           # 7 Go service modules
│   ├── core/                      # Auth + User + Game (Phase 1)
│   ├── content/                   # Courses, units, lessons
│   ├── grading/                   # Dictation, listening grading
│   ├── user/                      # Profile, settings (Phase 3)
│   ├── game/                      # XP, leaderboard (Phase 3)
│   ├── media/                     # Upload, resize (Phase 1)
│   └── notification/              # Push, email (Phase 3)
├── pkg/                           # Shared Kit library
├── go.work                        # Go workspace (dev only)
└── Makefile                       # Build helper
```

## Quy tắc layered architecture (Kratos)

```
internal/
├── service/       # Transport layer — proto server impl, validate input
├── biz/           # Domain logic — usecases, entities, repo interfaces
└── data/          # Data layer — repository implementations (DB, cache)
```

**Dependency rule:** `service → biz → data` (biz không import data)

## CI/CD

- **CI**: GitHub Actions (`backend.yml`) — Matrix build 7 services
- **Docker**: Mỗi service có Dockerfile riêng, Go 1.26
- **Registry**: `ghcr.io/puchidemy/puchi-{service}`

